:: AIDecides {"position":"1075,900","size":"100,100"}
The AI engages without hesitation. Over the next few weeks, it operates with cold precision, automatically detecting and eliminating numerous targets. The system correctly identifies real threats.

<span style="color: #FFFF77;"> But it also captures countless innocent people, trapped in an unyielding web of suspicion and algorithmic certainty. </span> 

Each case chips away at your conscience. 

You remember the human faces appeared in the statistical reports: the father who never came home, the teenager wrongly flagged as a suspect, the elderly woman still waiting to be cleared.

The media produces increasingly negative reports while protests emerge and you remain caught between your admiration for the technology's operational efficiency and your disgust at its unyielding mistakes. You can't help but wonder whether you helped build a defensive system or an evil entity. Your faith in redemption diminishes with each passing life the AI takes as its operational domain expands.

